          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/370_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Mix the <strong>lamb mixture</strong> thoroughly until fully combined, then shape into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> meatballs (clean hands is the best way!) – these are your <strong>rosemary lamb meatballs</strong></p><p>Refrigerate the meatballs until later</p><p>Tip: Chilling the meatballs helps them keep their shape when cooking</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/370_step-4-x200.jpg",
